    {
      "id": "authorable-pieces-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Authorable Pieces",
      "position": {
        "x": -460,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Authorable Pieces\n\nThis graph names the first concrete pieces a node author can add to an otherwise empty node.\n\nRevision after review:\n- some earlier \"pieces\" were really render/runtime consequences\n- the better split is between **views**, **controls**, **ports**, and **affordances**\n- execution and navigation mostly live below or beside the node surface, not as independent surface pieces",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
