    {
      "id": "authorable-pieces-core-list",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "First Pieces List",
      "position": {
        "x": 140,
        "y": -120
      },
      "width": 440,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Revised Pieces List\n\n- `view surface`\n- `node controls`\n- `port declarations`\n- `drag affordance`\n- `resize affordance`\n- `panels / secondary views`\n\nThese are the pieces that actually seem authorable at the node surface level.\n\nDropped from the first draft as independent pieces:\n- `execution` -> handled by scripts/runtime\n- `navigation / reference` -> mostly edge/port behavior\n- `view / media` -> folded into `view surface`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
