      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## View Surface\n\nWhat looked like \"content\" is really the node's primary view.\n\nContent comes from views.\n\nExamples:\n- markdown body\n- rendered document surface\n- custom visual surface\n- embedded web/media surface",
