    {
      "id": "authorable-pieces-controls",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Node Controls",
      "position": {
        "x": 1040,
        "y": -220
      },
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Node Controls\n\nThese are the visible controls that ride on the node surface.\n\nExamples:\n- expand\n- navigate\n- small action buttons\n- compact mode toggles\n\nCurrent rule:\n- node controls are primarily **renderer/editor-provided**, not node-authored\n- they express how the editor is showing the node, not what the node fundamentally is\n\nThese are not the large secondary panels.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
