    {
      "id": "authorable-pieces-navigation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Panels / Secondary Views",
      "position": {
        "x": 1420,
        "y": 60
      },
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Panels / Secondary Views\n\nThis is the better home for what was previously called \"controls\" in the broader sense.\n\nExamples:\n- side panels exposed by a node\n- deeper editor/configuration surfaces\n- alternate views opened from the node\n\nCurrent rule:\n- these are just **view nodes in a graph**\n- scripts/editor call them when needed\n- do not invent a new panel primitive unless the existing convention stops working",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
