      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Not Surface Pieces\n\nThese matter, but they are probably not authorable node-surface pieces in the same sense:\n\n- `execution`\n  - handled by scripts/runtime\n- `navigation / reference`\n  - mostly edge behavior, sometimes delegated through port-style nodes\n\nImportant, yes. Surface pieces, probably not.",
