      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Authorship Split\n\n### Node-authored\n- `view surface`\n- `node controls`\n- `port declarations`\n- `panels / secondary views`\n\n### Editor conventions\n- `drag affordance`\n- `resize affordance`\n\nReasoning:\n- authors define what the node shows and exposes\n- the editor keeps movement and resizing consistent across node families",
